message.content: cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.NE. The paper focuses on improving dialogue generation by incorporating knowledge base question answering, which is a common topic in natural language processing (NLP) and artificial intelligence (AI) research. Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also involves neural network models, which are commonly used in machine learning (cs.LG) and deep learning (cs.NE) research. The use of knowledge matching and attention mechanisms also relates to information retrieval (cs.IR) research.
